René Lefèvre (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9_Lef%C3%A8vre_(actor) 0 René Lefèvre, born René Paul Louis Lefèvre, (6 March 1898 - 23 May 1991) was a French actor and writer. Throughout his career, he worked with several notable directors, like Jean Renoir, Jean-Pierre Melville, Jules Dassin, and René Clair.
